# Source-only submission allowlist.
# Everything is ignored by default so local datasets, PCAPs, generated CSVs,
# model binaries, stream output, caches, IDE files, and the separate report .tex
# do not appear in the GitHub sync.
*

# Keep folders explorable so allowlisted files inside them can be tracked.
!*/

# Root project files to publish.
!.gitignore
!README.md
!EDGE_IIOT_FULL_PROJECT_GUIDE.md
!TrainingResults.md
!environment-edgeids.yml
!run_live_demo.py

# Source files to publish.
!experment/edge_iiot_experiment.py
!spark_streaming/edge_ids_stream.py
!spark_streaming/ids_dashboard.py
!testoutside/live_wifi_edge_ids.py
!testoutside/live_wifi_edge_ids_pcap.py
